    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine <strong>half</strong> your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with your <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>honey harissa dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1624609783113-x200.jpg",
